Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Razbio* sam čašu dok sam prao sudove. (I broke a glass while doing the dishes.)
2. On je već *razbio* pet prozora u zgradi. (He has already broken five windows in the building.)
3. Nisam mogao da verujem kada sam video da su lopovi *razbili* bravu na vratima. (I couldn't believe it when I saw that the burglars had broken the lock on the door.)
4. Čim je čuo lošu vest, *razbio* je flašu o zid. (As soon as he heard the bad news, he smashed a bottle against the wall.)
5. Sinoć je veliki talas *razbio* deo obale. (Last night a big wave smashed part of the coastline.)
6. Moj prijatelj je *razbio* ugovor sa svojim poslodavcem. (My friend broke his contract with his employer.)
7. *Razbij* jaja i stavi ih u činiju. (Crack the eggs and put them in a bowl.)
8. Ne želim da *razbijem* prijateljstvo sa tobom. (I don't want to break our friendship.)
9. Kada je video da ne može da popravi auto, *razočarano je odustao* i pozvao šlep službu. (When he saw that he couldn't fix the car, he gave up disappointedly and called the tow truck.)

Note: The word "razbio" can have different meanings depending on the context. In the examples above, it can mean "to break," "to smash," "to shatter," "to cancel," "to disappoint," "to crack," "to give up disappointedly," etc.